---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1 class="hero-name">L. June Bloch</h1>
      <p class="hero-identity">Anthropologist · Ethnic Studies · Builder</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">
        I don't just write about how systems produce violence — I build the tools that
        redesign them. Same critical theory, same analytical practice: the publications
        are in the field's top journals, the software runs from the frameworks those
        publications develop.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-socials">
        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=9bQ8kjIAAAAJ&hl=en&oi=ao" aria-label="Google Scholar">Scholar</a>
        <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/disabledbydesign.bsky.social" aria-label="Bluesky">Bluesky</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/grouchyseafowl" aria-label="GitHub">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/l-june-bloch-1897a329/" aria-label="LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="mailto:june@ljunebloch.com" aria-label="Email">june@ljunebloch.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img
        src="/images/headshot-rect.png"
        alt="Dr. L. June Bloch"
        width="280"
        height="350"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <a href="/research/" class="feature-link">
        <h3>Research</h3>
        <p>An elder said: "Did you ever consider that it isn't a bird?" It was a moth. That question reorganized fifteen years of fieldwork and five research programs.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/publications/" class="feature-link">
        <h3>Publications</h3>
        <p><em>Cultural Anthropology</em>, <em>American Anthropologist</em>, <em>Current Anthropology</em> — recognition, animacy, settler colonialism, genocide, algorithmic justice, Indigenous knowledge, trans studies, and the politics of care.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/projects/" class="feature-link">
        <h3>Software</h3>
        <p>"Output format is the activation function for bias." Seven open-source tools built from critical theory, zero dollars of tech funding.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/teaching/" class="feature-link">
        <h3>Teaching</h3>
        <p>Ethnic Studies was created by student strikes. The pedagogy should honor that — consensus-based, horizontal, survivable. No late penalties, reading equivalencies, emergency flex weeks.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>


</BaseLayout>
